<!-- pages/user/user.wxml -->
<view class="card">
  <view class="icon-logo">
    <image src="../../../image/icon-logo.png"></image>
  </view>
  <view class="hd">
    <view class="tit">可用余额:</view>
    <view class="flex-center info">
      <view class="money">{{show?balance+"元":"******"}}<text></text></view>
      <view class="show" bindtap="changeMoney">
        <text class="iconfont icon-eye" wx:if="{{show}}"></text>
        <text class="iconfont icon-eye2" wx:else></text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="myline">
    <image src="../../../image/myline.png" style="height:40rpx"></image>
  </view>
  <view class="active flex-center" wx:if="{{!subscribe}}" bind:tap="toPro">
    <view>
      <view>请先关注原麦官方公众号再付款，成功后可得原麦红包奖励哦～</view>
      <text>关注原麦山丘</text>
    </view>
    <view class="wxbtn">去关注</view>
  </view>
  <view class="card-info">
    <view class="card-code">NO.{{card_no}}</view>
    <view class="card-code-img">
      <canvas canvas-id="barcode"></canvas>
    </view>
    <view class="txt">扫码付款</view>
  </view>
  <view class="tips"><text class="iconfont icon-notice2"></text> 原麦山丘动物园店、十里堡门店暂不支持会员余额支付给您带来不便请谅解！</view>
</view>

<view class="fixedBtn" style="padding-bottom:{{btmHolder}}px">
  <view class="btn" bindtap="toAccount">余额充值</view>
</view>
<view style="height:{{56+btmHolder}}px"></view>